Dependencies:
-------------

Use need to use the xlrd library, so:
$> sudo apt-get install python-xlrd

OR

$> sudo easy_install xlrd

Using the scripts:
-----------------

./flxcore_product_import.py -s localhost -p 8069 -u admin -w PASSWORD -d DATABASE_NAME file_to_import.xls

-s: specify the OpenERP server hostname
-p: specify the OpenERP XMLRPC port number
-u: specify the OpenERP username for connecting
-w: specify the OpenERP password for connecting
-d: specify the OpenERP database on which we're going to work

file_to_import.xls: must be a MS Excel 97/2003 file.
